description:
This is a 6 minute workout called '4-7-8 Calm Breathing Exercise I 5 Minute Guided Breathwork to Relax or Fall Asleep Fast' from the channel Breathe With Sandy.
The workout falls under Rest/Breathing exercises and Rest/Meditation.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Deep Recharge and The Sleep Prep vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

The 4-7-8 breathing technique can help calm your sympathetic nervous system, which controls your fight-or-flight response. The music is here to guide you along and you can do this exercise whenever you feel stressed or want to fall asleep faster.
